/////////////////
// Installation
/////////////////
[For windows:]
Precompiled installers can be found here:
- http://www.lfd.uci.edu/~gohlke/pythonlibs/

Install:
- python-2.7 32bit
- pygame-1.9.1.win32-py2.7
- PIL-1.1.7.win32-py2.7
- opencv-python-2.4.4.win32-py2.7
- numpy-MKL-1.7.0.win32-py2.7

[For Linux:]
sudo apt-get install python python-opencv python-pygame python-imaging

